file.name: openapi.yaml
file.content:
openapi: 3.0.0
servers:
  - url: 'http://127.0.0.1:8080'
info:
  title: 'Callback'
  version: '1'
  description: 'Callback test'
  contact:
    name: Test User
    url: https://example.com
    email: test@example.com
tags:
  - name: callbackEx
    description: Callback Example
paths:
  /hooks:
    post:
      operationId: postHook
      summary: POST to hooks
      tags:
      - callbackEx
      requestBody:
        $ref: '#/components/requestBodies/HooksPost'
      responses:
        '201':
          description: 'Successfully registered'
      callbacks:
        data_event:
          $ref: '#/components/callbacks/DataEvent'
components:
  callbacks:
    DataEvent:
      '{$request.body#/callbackUrl}':
        post:
          operationId: callbackPost
          summary: Callback POST operation
          requestBody:
            $ref: '#/components/requestBodies/CallBackBody'
          responses:
            '200':
              description: 'Your callback should answer with 200'
  requestBodies:
    HooksPost:
        content:
          application/json:
            schema:
              type: object
              required:
               - callbackUrl
              properties:
                callbackUrl:
                  type: string
    CallBackBody:
      content:
        application/json:
          schema:
            required:
              - subscriptionId
            type: object
            properties:
              subscriptionId:
                type: string
